query:
select name, stars, full_address, takes_reservations, categories, wifi, touristy, casual, price_range, latitude, longitude from yelp join perks join ambience
where (price_range = 2) and (yelp.business_id = perks.b_id and yelp.business_id = ambience.b_id) and (categories like '%chinese%' or categories like '%italian%' or categories like '%pizza%'
or perks.wifi = 1 or perks.takes_reservations = 1
or ambience.touristy = 1 or ambience.casual = 1) order by stars desc;
